## Third-Party Dependencies

This project uses only Python standard library components:
- asyncio (Python 3.7+)
- sqlite3 (Built-in)
- subprocess (Built-in)
- json (Built-in)
- pathlib (Built-in)
- hashlib (Built-in)
- logging (Built-in)

No external dependencies are required.

## AppleScript Integration

This software integrates with:
- DEVONthink 3 (DEVONtechnologies, LLC)
- Zotero (Corporation for Digital Scholarship)

Both applications maintain their own licensing terms. This software does not modify or redistribute any components of these applications.

## Data Privacy

DEVONzot operates entirely locally on your Mac:
- No cloud services are used
- No data is transmitted over the internet  
- All metadata operations remain on your local system
- Database access is read-only for Zotero
- File operations respect existing permissions

Your research data privacy is fully preserved.